remove beta2AR and resn SO4+BU1+ACM+GLC
remove muOR    and resn SO4+MPG+CL
remove A2AR    and resn SO4
remove kappaOR and resn CIT+PEG

hide everything

# block 4
show cartoon, bRho    and polymer
show cartoon, beta2AR and polymer
show cartoon, muOR    and polymer
show cartoon, A2AR    and polymer
show cartoon, kappaOR and polymer

# block 5
color marine,    bRho    and polymer
color forest,    beta2AR and polymer
color raspberry, muOR    and polymer
color orange,    A2AR    and polymer
color purple,    kappaOR and polymer

# block 6
